<h1 style="text-align: center"><b>Welcome to the FreeREG Registration process.</b></h1>
<p>Through this process you may register with FreeREG either as a <b>transcriber</b>, or express a willingness to join FreeREG in a <b>technical</b> capacity. </p>




<p><b>Transcriber: </b> As a transcriber you can register to join a team of transcribers focused on a specific region or type of record.The list of You will be assigned to a Syndicate Coordinator who will guide and help you, assign you work and take you through any required training. 
If you are uncertain on the team you wish to join or require additional information before making a final decision you can still register and have our volunteer coordinator discuss transcribing with you and have them assign you to the best fit. In which case select the General syndicate when selecting a syndicate.</p>


<p><b>Technical: </b>If you have an interest in joining the technical team then register and a member of the executive will get in touch with you to see how you may be able to contribute. We are specifically interested in people with experience in Rails/Ruby technology and html/css coding.</p>


